55_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2019-11-23/20191123-145555-P_20191123_145555_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"総持寺前のカフェ1\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2019-11-23/20191123-145634-P_20191123_145634_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2019-11-23/20191123-145634-P_20191123_145634_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"総持寺前のカフェ2\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>終着の穴水駅<br>\n<a href=\"2019-11-23/20191123-161829-P_20191123_161829_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2019-11-23/20191123-161829-P_20191123_161829_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"穴水駅\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2020-08-05T11:50:21","published":"2019-12-20T03:29:08"}